lombok-slf4j - Lombok SLF4J Fixer

USAGE:
    lombok-slf4j <source-filename>

DESCRIPTION:
    Replace manual SLF4J logger with Lombok @Slf4j annotation.
    Removes logger declarations and adds annotation.

ARGUMENTS:
    source-filename
        Java source file to fix (required)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-lombok-slf4j-logger-name NAME
        Logger name to use (default: log)

EXAMPLES:
    lombok-slf4j MyClass.java
    lombok-slf4j src/main/java/com/example/Service.java
